examples.en: Mobile phones have become an indispensable part of our lives.
This book is indispensable to anyone interested in space exploration.
Those were the indispensable means to our end.
Meat is not indispensable for maintaining a healthy diet.
The keeping of the proprieties is as indispensable as clean linen.
Fully aware that he was an indispensable assistant, he decided that it was high time that he be paid what he was worth.
